The canonical FeatureOps agent guidelines for this repository are in `AGENTS.md` — treat
that file as the single source of truth and apply it to every change.

@../../AGENTS.md

Quick reminders:

- Flag-gate risky changes, especially payments (the seam is `src/gift-store/checkout/payments/router.ts`).
- Flag naming: `p<NNN>_<rl|ex|op|kx|pm>_[v_]<domain>_<component>_<slug>`.
- Always name the project id (`project-NNN`) on MCP flag operations — there is no default project.
- PayBro and Dashed are real payment providers, not mocks.
